A_N = N \cdot A_{N-1} + (-1)^N = N \cdot (N-1)! \cdot \left(\sum_{i = 0}^{N-1} \frac{(-1)^i}{i!}\right) + N! \frac{(-1)^N}{N!}
 = N! \cdot \left(\sum_{i = 0}^{N - 1} \frac{(-1)^i}{i!} + \frac{(-1)^N}{N!}\right) = N! \cdot \sum_{i = 0}^{N} \frac{(-1)^i}{i!}
